data.title: Official Emerson, Lake & Palmer Store
data.meta_description: Carl Palmer Fanfare for The Common Man 3CD Blu Ray + Book Box Set out now
data.text:
Includes Exclusive 23” x 11" folded poster, free with every double LP purchased (while stocks last).

Legendary progressive rock giants Emerson, Lake & Palmer were formed in 1970 and are regarded as one of the most successful rock bands of the 1970s, ELP’s first 7 albums reached U.K. Top 10 and U.S. Top 20.

ELP are torchbearers of the progressive rock sound and jointly created the supergroup concept. They are among the most important bands in the history of rock music, helping to broaden the genre audience into tens of millions.

This 2LP gatefold ‘Ultimate Collection’ is the perfect release for new fans who want an overview of who ELP were and what they stood for and existi...
